For new projects:
    1. git init  ===> "Initialize Repository" in the source control section"
    2. git add . ===> "+" symbol in the source control section
    3. git commit -m "commitMessage" ===> "Commit" button in source control section
    4. git branch -M master & git remote add ===> "..." in source control section -> remote  -> add remote
    5. git push ===> publish branch in source control section -> "..." in source section